  "description": "Replaces mace with wind hammer texture",
  "body": "\n![Top Bar](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6fcfeba3062c7f63bc89e40a763023757f45ea1c.png)\n\n\n\\\nMaces look very heavy, unhandy and slow... so we replaced them with Windhammers! Not Warhammers! >:C\n\nHave fun with timing your next bash!  \n  \n<br/><br/>\n\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/963ed054af52d4cd8f7c2d9a38c03507dee0fb50.png\">\n</p><p align=\"center\">\nComparison of mace textures (vanilla) and windhammer from pack\n</p>\n\n<br/><br/>\n**Supported languages:**\n- English (en_us)\n- Polish (pl_pl)\n- LOLcat (lol_us)\n- Silesian (szl)\n\n\n<br/><br/>\n### Follow us on other platforms!\n<br/><br/>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/hisho/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a279e0c91678e4c5dcf40e2b493c18be18f0ff83_0.webp\">\n&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Lobster_Project\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b0aeaaa86664636b3aef17480e3f43e7bcff8b0b.png\"> &emsp;<a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/lobsterproject.bsky.social\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/962d0a69aaf1855c89a0961d96f0d0ca6146a517.png\">\n</p>",
